<section id="main-content" class="main-content large-8 columns">
<article class="">
<div class="article-title-wrapper">
<h1>
How to Make Best Use of Instagram Stories Stickers for Marketing
</h1>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="byline-large-2 columns">
<div class="article-byline">
<div class="author">
<h4 class="hide-small byline-show-large">Author</h4>
<span class="byline-hide-large">By</span>
<div class="author-name">
<a rel="author" href="/users/abrooks/">
Aaron Brooks
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="date">
<div class="published-info">
<h4>Published</h4>
Feb. 7, 2019
</div>
</div>
<div class="social-share">
<h4 class="hide-small byline-show-large">Share it</h4>
<ul class="rrssb-buttons clearfix">
<li class="rrssb-linkedin">
